<!-- File-upload — spec card render
     Source spec: ds-architect-agent/children/components/forms.md#file-upload -->
<div class="dst-component-card">
  <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">File-upload</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">3 variants · 3 sizes · 6 states</p>
  </div>
  <p class="dst-component-intro">Drag-and-drop + click-to-browse upload zone. Lists uploaded files with per-item progress.</p>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Variants</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">default · single</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">multiple · file list</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">image · with thumbnails</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Sizes</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">sm · 120px tall</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">md · 160px tall</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">lg · 240px tall</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">States</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">idle</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">dragOver</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">uploading</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">success</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">error</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">disabled</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-note"><strong>Behavior:</strong> drag&drop + click-to-browse · per-file progress bar (uses <code>progress.linear</code>) · cancel + retry icon-buttons trailing each row · <code>accept</code> filters MIME types · <code>maxSize</code> + <code>maxFiles</code> validate before upload starts.</div>
</div>
